&lt;a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/script/type/importmap" 
 target="_blank" 
 rel="noopener">import maps
&lt;/a> from your &lt;code>package.json&lt;/code>, enabling bare module specifiers in your demos.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="what-are-import-maps">What Are Import Maps?&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Import maps let you use package names in imports instead of full paths:&lt;/p>

&lt;code-highlighter>
 &lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-js" data-lang="js">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">// With import maps:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kr">import&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">LitElement&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">from&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;lit&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">// Without import maps:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kr">import&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">LitElement&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">from&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;../node_modules/lit/index.js&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>
&lt;/code-highlighter>&lt;h2 id="automatic-generation">Automatic Generation&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>The dev server reads your &lt;code>package.json&lt;/code> and generates an import map for all dependencies:&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>package.json:&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>

&lt;code-highlighter>
 &lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-json" data-lang="json">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;dependencies&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;lit&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;^3.0.0&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;@patternfly/elements&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;^3.0.0&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>
